SUMMARY:cherry presents: "for the eldest daughters only" walk
LOCATION:Little Marina Green Picnic Area\, San Francisco\, CA
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nOur first eldest daughters event completely ble
 w up with HUNDREDS of women on the waitlist. It clearly struck a chord\, w
 hich told us everything we needed to know.\n\nSo\, we're opening it up to 
 all eldest daughters in SF! No cap\, no list to get off of. Just come as y
 ou are <3\n\nWe'll kick things off with a few low-key exercises so you can
  actually meet the people around you (no awkward name-tag energy\, promise
 ) — and then we will collectively swarm the San Francisco Bay Trail in d
 roves at sunset walk along the water. It may be the most powerful walk in 
 Bay Area history...\n\nHere's what to bring:\n\n👯 A fellow eldest daugh
 ter friend (or come solo and make one)\n\n🫶 Yourself\, exactly as you a
 re\n\nThat's it. I genuinely can't wait to meet my kindred spirits in pers
 on! Already counting down the days!\n\nCan't make it? Fill this out anyway
 s.\n\nXO\,\n\nAnna\, founder of Cherry\n\nCherry is a women's health brand
  building things we actually want to use + a community of women who get it
 . You can follow along on Instagram\, TikTok\, and join our waitlist for t
 he first product drop.\n\nCalendar: cherry community\n\nHosts: Anna Nicker
 son\n\nVenue: Little Marina Green Picnic Area\n\nEvent page: https://luma.
 com/p8vl0pqz
