 ssed with metrics. It tracks strength training\, Pilates\, fitness classes
 \, recovery\, sleep\, steps\, and HRV\, then translates it into simple gui
 dance on consistency\, progress\, and recovery.\n\nMiranda Nover\, Founder
  of Fort\, will join Volume 4 to discuss how Fort is helping bridge the ga
 p between working out and building real strength.\n\nFort will also offer 
 live demos of beta devices\, with the technical team on-site to answer que
 stions about how wearables work and how to get the most out of yours.\n\nA
 ttendees receive:\n\nComplimentary 2-day Equinox gym pass\n\nDiscounts on 
