SUMMARY:CISO Roundtable Dinner
LOCATION:Los Altos Hills\, Palo Alto\, CA
DESCRIPTION:Source: Cerebral Valley\n\nSenior security leaders will gather 
 for an intimate dinner where Caroline Wong—author of the Cybersecurity C
 anon Hall of Fame-inducted "Security Metrics" and former CISO at eBay\, Sy
 mantec\, and Cobalt—kicks off a candid roundtable conversation about AI 
 risk\, agent governance\, and the evolving pressures of modern security le
 adership. It's a small-room peer discussion with no vendor pitches\, just 
 CISOs and their counterparts wrestling with what's actually keeping them u
