 at supercharge biomedical discovery\, creating MCP agents and workflows th
 at extend AI capabilities for biological reasoning and hypothesis generati
 on. Owkin's infrastructure and their AI Scientist K Pro provide a rare pla
 yground for exploring how AI genuinely accelerates research.\n\nEvent page
