SUMMARY:The Fermi Qualifier (A) - 24hr Hack: $25K Cash + Nvidia Supercomput
 er
LOCATION:San Francisco\, CA
DESCRIPTION:Source: Cerebral Valley\n\nA high-stakes 24-hour qualifier hack
 athon focused on long-horizon agent reliability and judgment will bring to
 gether skilled AI developers competing for a $25\,000 prize and an NVIDIA 
