SUMMARY:Design Meetup x Google Sunnyvale\, CA: At Scale
LOCATION:Sunnyvale\, CA
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nJoin us AT SCALE — Design Meetup x Google!\n\
 nWe'll start the night with food and drinks\, followed by a series of inte
 ractive lightning talks and an exclusive "Ask me anything!" Q&A. Our speak
 ers will dive into the behind-the-scenes of projects and workflows they've
  built\, showing how to upskill as the next generation of builders and how
  their own workflows have changed recently.\n\nFeaturing:\n\nJennifer Jing
 \, Designer @ YouTube\n\nZhengnan Zhao\, Designer\, Creator\, Builder @ Yo
 uTube\n\nJaime Sonoda\, Design Manager\, YouTube Shorts and Gen AI @ YouTu
 be\n\nShawn Carter\, Senior Designer @ Gemini Enterprise\n\nCarsten Hinz\,
  Product Experience Lead @ Gemini Enterprise\n\nTian Deng\, Staff UX Desig
 ner @ Gemini Enterprise\n\nSheta Chatterjee\, Senior Director\, UX @ Cloud
  AI\n\nSönke Rohde\, Principal UX Designer @ Cloud AI\n\nDevon Wang\, Sen
 ior UX Designer @ Cloud AI\n\nSchedule\n\n5:30 PM: Doors Open · Food + Dr
 inks\n\n6:00 PM: Intros to Design Meetup (Doors close at 6:30 sharp)\n\n6:
 10 PM: 2 Lightning Presentations\n\n6:40 PM: Quick Break\n\n6:50 PM: Ask M
 e Anything with Designers from the Gemini Enterprise Team\n\n7:10 PM: Open
  Networking\n\n8:00 PM: Closing\n\nWho this is for\nStudents and early-to-
 mid career designers navigating their careers.\n\nBy attending\, you give 
 your consent to be photographed or filmed. If you prefer not to be include
 d\, please notify us during check-in or adjust your RSVP.\n\nSee you at AT
  SCALE — Google x Design Meetup! ✨\n\nFollow us on Instagram: @designm
 eetup\nFollow us on X: @designmeetuphq\n\nCalendar: Design Meetup\n\nHosts
 : Ilyssa Yan\, Shawn Carter\n\nEvent page: https://luma.com/b6gce78l
URL:https://luma.com/b6gce78l
