 ing hard problems.\n\nWe're backing you with some of the best teams:\n\nAW
 S: the models and cloud infrastructure to help you actually ship\n\nZero.x
 yz: unblocks your AI for free\n\nNexla: the data layer for AI - connectivi
 ty\, context\, and data delivery built for enterprise AI systems.\n\nPomer
 ium: Secure your agentic runtime\n\nSpeakers\n\nWe have an incredible line
 up of speakers and judges that will be present at the event.\n\nMichael Lu
 dden - Marketing @ ZeroClick\n\nAbhijit Bharadwaj - Software AI Engineer @
