SUMMARY:AGI Summit 2026 Hackathon
LOCATION:Palace of Fine Arts\, San Francisco\, CA
DESCRIPTION:Source: Cerebral Valley\n\nBuilders and AI innovators will tack
 le autonomous intelligence in a 2-day hackathon\, shipping AI agents\, mul
 ti-agent systems\, and autonomous workflows while competing for up to $1\,
 000 in prizes. Engineers\, founders\, and researchers will collaborate to 
