LOCATION:550 Laguna St\, San Francisco\, CA
DESCRIPTION:Source: Cerebral Valley\n\nPeople building anything—from code
  to art to companies—will spend their evening working side-by-side in fo
 cused sprints\, breaking isolation with spontaneous collaboration and a sh
 are-back where everyone learns from what stuck or got built. It's less net
